title: Between You And Us: Episode 12
description:
Greetings from the Schiefer Sisters! We're back for another episode where we read reviews sent in by you, our lovely listeners! So stop smelling horses and put down your pizza rolls, because something is rotten in the State of Yelp... Enjoy!
Go watch our latest YouTube video to see us reveal the man behind the intro: youtu.be/l8Qzn-kW2wY
Buy our merch! https://store.dftba.com/collections/beach-too-sandy-water-too-wet
Logo by Courtney DeKorte. Theme by Mavus White.
Music by PSOVOD and tyops.
